## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all recent studies or data. The classification of clinical vulnerability can vary based on evolving health guidelines and individual health assessments. Additionally, the information is subject to change as new research emerges, particularly concerning COVID-19 and its impact on people with diabetes.

